subject: Great speaking with you - Fareed Aziz
body:
Hi Fareed,

Great connecting today! Thanks for taking the time to walk through your current outbound setup and goals.

**Quick Recap:**
• Discussed your current lead generation challenges
• Reviewed our multi-channel approach (Email → LinkedIn → Calling)
• Covered our TAM coverage model (reaching every decision-maker every 45-60 days)

**Next Steps:**
• I'll send over a proposal outlining how we'd approach your specific market
• We can schedule a follow-up call once you've had a chance to review

**Recording:**
Here's the link to our conversation for your reference: https://fathom.video/calls/543681319

Looking forward to working together!

Best,
Liam

---
Liam Sheridan
Leads That Show
leadsthat.show
